14#include <config.h>
15
16#include <stdio.h>
17
18#include <isc/md.h>
19#include <isc/util.h>
20
21#include <openssl/evp.h>
22#include <openssl/err.h>
23#include <openssl/opensslv.h>
24
25#include "openssl_shim.h"
26
27isc_md_t *
28isc_md_new(void) {
29 isc_md_t *md = EVP_MD_CTX_new();
30 RUNTIME_CHECK(md != NULL);
31 return (md);
32}
33
34void
35isc_md_free(isc_md_t *md) {
36 if (ISC_UNLIKELY(md == NULL)) {
37 return;
38 }
39
40 EVP_MD_CTX_free(md);
41}
42
43isc_result_t
44isc_md_init(isc_md_t *md, const isc_md_type_t md_type) {
45 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
46
47 if (md_type == NULL) {
48 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
49 }
50
51 if (EVP_DigestInit_ex(md, md_type, NULL) != 1) {
52 return (ISC_R_CRYPTOFAILURE);
53 }
54
55 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
56}
57
58isc_result_t
59isc_md_reset(isc_md_t *md) {
60 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
61
62 if (EVP_MD_CTX_reset(md) != 1) {
63 return (ISC_R_CRYPTOFAILURE);
64 }
65
66 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
67}
68
69isc_result_t
70isc_md_update(isc_md_t *md, const unsigned char *buf, const size_t len) {
71 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
72
73 if (ISC_UNLIKELY(buf == NULL || len == 0)) {
74 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
75 }
76
77 if (EVP_DigestUpdate(md, buf, len) != 1) {
78 return (ISC_R_CRYPTOFAILURE);
79 }
80
81 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
82}
83
84isc_result_t
85isc_md_final(isc_md_t *md, unsigned char *digest, unsigned int *digestlen) {
86 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
87 REQUIRE(digest != NULL);
88
89 if (EVP_DigestFinal_ex(md, digest, digestlen) != 1) {
90 return (ISC_R_CRYPTOFAILURE);
91 }
92
93 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
94}
95
96isc_md_type_t
97isc_md_get_md_type(isc_md_t *md) {
98 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
99
100 return (EVP_MD_CTX_md(md));
101}
102
103size_t
104isc_md_get_size(isc_md_t *md) {
105 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
106
107 return (EVP_MD_CTX_size(md));
108}
109
110size_t
111isc_md_get_block_size(isc_md_t *md) {
112 REQUIRE(md != NULL);
113
114 return (EVP_MD_CTX_block_size(md));
115}
116
117size_t
118isc_md_type_get_size(isc_md_type_t md_type) {
119 if (md_type != NULL) {
120 return ((size_t)EVP_MD_size(md_type));
121 }
122
123 return (ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE);
124}
125
126size_t
127isc_md_type_get_block_size(isc_md_type_t md_type) {
128 if (md_type != NULL) {
129 return ((size_t)EVP_MD_block_size(md_type));
130 }
131
132 return (ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE);
133}
134
135isc_result_t
136isc_md(isc_md_type_t md_type, const unsigned char *buf, const size_t len,
137 unsigned char *digest, unsigned int *digestlen)
138{
139 isc_md_t *md;
140 isc_result_t res;
141
142 md = isc_md_new();
143
144 res = isc_md_init(md, md_type);
145 if (res != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
146 goto end;
147 }
148
149 res = isc_md_update(md, buf, len);
150 if (res != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
151 goto end;
152 }
153
154 res = isc_md_final(md, digest, digestlen);
155 if (res != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
156 goto end;
157 }
158 end:
159 isc_md_free(md);
160
161 return (res);
162}
